  "text": "Our assay system is well-established in research on endothelial cell apoptosis [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . In the present pilot study this assay system seems promising for further elucidation of the biological consequences of CPB. Endothelial cell apoptosis is able to explain many adverse effects of CPB. Further insight into the causative mechanisms and possibly antiapoptotic treatment may result in reduction of the whole body in¯ammatory response to CPB and ultimately in better clinical results.",
